{"tid":1383622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無諗過不停換戰線 打真游擊？","createTime":"2019-07-29T17:29:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T12:37:02.000Z","uid":168228,"like":127,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"6bddb81f35c666b68135ca144ee06d6cd0df3055","tid":1383622,"uid":168228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:29:33.000Z","msg":"睇完天琦篇野 <br />\n點先可以對抗啲狗之餘不受傷不被捕？<br />\n<br />\n突然諗到 如果好似728 根本無目標<br />\n咁不如set防線 有狗推進就換戰線<br />\n以中環為例 可以轉去金鐘灣仔<br />\n撚狗之餘又唔會受傷 仲可以擴大戰線(一般民眾)<br />\n<br />\n唔知有無得諗？"},{"pid":"b55a157e542ad9dfac58399538a485fc2f4831f3","tid":1383622,"uid":168228,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:32:15.000Z","msg":"啲狗又捉你唔到 又無得部署下一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90957bfa066335d42405ca7041b08504294a133c","tid":1383622,"uid":168228,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:33:10.000Z","msg":"勇武又可以留力<br />\n和理非又唔洗咁驚有事"},{"pid":"854857dec28d75614bcb05076e44dbf8de26fa53","tid":1383622,"uid":53808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:34:38.000Z","msg":"互推<br />\n<br />\n[警世] 用啱方法救藍絲老豆老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382086\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382086</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"7d09d6889857000c560c5a5eea0bf5edef3152c3","tid":1383622,"uid":53922,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:36:18.000Z","msg":"我見遮打個日有班和理非真係唔夠膽行出公園，因為話出公園集會係非法...<br />\n<br />\n咁你話有幾多和理非會咁勇周圍行？"},{"pid":"d3c2c9a17bb42e034e347a170312ea9f4556f48f","tid":1383622,"uid":198461,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:37:27.000Z","msg":"PUsh,<br />\n深縱作戰，大範圍遊擊係好野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遊擊作戰，最大既好處係冇設防負擔，將主力化整為0，再分割圍殲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我最愛既毛主席係咁講"},{"pid":"cd399a6c1aaf7afb331c18ab4eb528ecee428b6